                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.5045/218: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">MacMurray</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-09-11T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 11, 1925—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>241. Your 389, September 10, 5 p.m. You may inform British Chargé that assurance
                    is satisfactory, and that you are ready to proceed with negotiations with
                    Chinese Government regarding Shanghai incident.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
